T1  - HOUSING DECISION WITH DIVORCE RISK
AU  - Fischer, Marcel
AU  - Khorunzhina, Natalia
Y1  - 2019/08/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12385
